node.text: ⚠️AMAZING KITTEN RESCUE!⚠️ During our recent trip to Greece, our friends @everchanginghorizon and @jess.wandering rescued the cutest little kitten that was abandoned on a cliffside and we were honored to also help after getting introduced to @zawf.zante.gr an incredible animal rescue charity that desperately needed more funding to help save more animals! Karmagawa cofounder @timothysykes donated 1,000 euros to them on the spot, but we have also created a fundraiser with the goal of raising $25,000 to get them a full on shelter and veterinarian on their staff because there are SO many more animals in Zakynthos that need URGENT help so please donate what you can, share this video with your followers and tag people, celebrities and influencers who need to see and share this too and let’s all work together to raise the $25k ZAWF needs to help more animals in need! Sadly, this little kitten didn’t make it and that’s why we MUST get these poor animals more help faster in the future…we’ll link our @karmagawa Facebook fundraiser in our stories/highlights too and ALL donations on all platforms, great and small, are most appreciated! #helpanimals #savethekitties #zakynthos #animalrescue #karmagawa

node.text: ⚠️HOW GREAT IS THIS ANIMAL RESCUE?!⚠️ Leo found this squirrel having a seizure while he was helping his mom in the garden and he quickly decided to help this poor creature in need. Even though the squirrel was unresponsive at first, Leo still wanted to help and as you watch this video, see how he and his sister successfully nursed this poor squirrel back to full health! How great is this?! Please share this heartwarming video with your followers and tag people who need some positivity in their day and let’s all thank Leo and his sister for their amazing animal rescue here as we should all get inspired to help animals in need! Great video @ladbible #saveanimals #animalrescue #helpanimals #karmagawa

node.text: ⚠️GRAPHIC IMAGES: PLEASE SHARE THIS AND SIGN THE PETITION TO STOP THIS ANIMAL ABUSE RIGHT NOW! ⚠️ Do you know the dark truth behind the cosmetic industry and the beauty products far too many unaware people use? How beautiful can someone feel if they knew that their beauty products caused unimaginable pain and torture to innocent animals?⁣⁠ The testing of baby pigs, beagles, rabbits, monkeys, rats and mice reveals deliberate cruelty…rabbits dying, monkeys screaming and dogs suffering accompanied by staff jokes as they are injected or forced to ingest or inhale substances to measure toxic effects, which can include vomiting, internal bleeding, respiratory problems, fever, organ failure and even death.⁠ This happens worldwide and spreading awareness is the key to stopping it so please share this sad post with your followers and tag people who need to see this. There’s also a petition in the @karmagawa highlights to close Vivotecnia Laboratory, one of the worst offenders...THIS MUST STOP NOW! Please share this video with your followers and tag people, celebrities and influencers who need to see this too and sign the petition we’ve linked in our highlights as sadly more than 115 million animals suffer and die every year in laboratories like these — WE MUST WORK TOGETHER TO STOP THIS ANIMAL ABUSE RIGHT NOW!  Use your social media platform and share to speak up for these innocent animals that are being tortured! Eye-opening video by @thesavemovement  #endanimalcruelty #stopanimalcruelty #endanimaltesting #stopanimaltesting #animalsdeservebetter #karmagawa

node.title: The Dark Truth Behind The Cosmetic Industry

node.text: ⚠️PLEASE SHARE THIS AMAZING VIDEO AND LET’S REMIND EVERYONE TO HELP ANIMALS IN NEED! ⚠️ This rescued baby chimp fell asleep in the lap of the pilot @anthonycaere while they flew to his new home…how cute is this?! Amazing work Anthony and @lwiro_primates stop, ok ease help us get the word out about this incredible story and these people who work hard to protect these beautiful animals by sharing this post and tagging people who need to see it as we MUST make this a better planet for humans and animals alike and spreading awareness is the key! Great video by @thedodo #animalrescue #savethebabies #animalsdeservebetter #stopthekilling #karmagawa

node.text: ⚠️GRAPHIC WARNING: PLEASE SHARE TO HELP STOP THIS REVOLTING ANIMAL CRUELTY! ⚠️ This is who really suffers for the exotic skins trade. This footage exposes how workers are trained to kill and skin crocodiles—all for “fashion” and WE MUST EACH DO OUR PART TO STOP THIS MADNESS RIGHT NOW! The fact that people still buy clothing and accessories made from animal skin like this is due to a lack of awareness of how terribly these animals are treated so please use your social media platform and share this URGENT video with your followers to help us educate everyone as WE MUST STOP THIS ANIMAL ABUSE ONCE AND FOR ALL! There’s plenty of other non-cruel materials that can be used to make clothing and accessories, especially sustainable/recycled fabrics like our own Karmagawa & @savethereef charity march (see link in our bio)…WE MUST GET THE FASHION INDUSTRY TO STOP ABUSING/ELECTROCUTING INNOCENT ANIMALS! Please share this sad video and tag people, celebrities, influencers & news media who need to see and share this too…no animal deserves to to be treated like this! Thanks for posting @peta #savethecrocodiles #endanimalcruelty #stopanimalcruelty #karmagawa

node.title: Why You Shouldn’t Buy Crocodile Skin Clothing/Accessories

node.text: ⚠️HOW AMAZING IS THIS ACT OF HUMAN KINDNESS?⚠️This cow had fallen down a slope and into the fast-moving water and would have drowned had it not been saved by several brave locals here. Please watch and share this incredible animal rescue video with your followers and tag people, celebrities, influencers and news media who need to see it so they can share too & let’s all spread awareness about this important message of how we should ALL help animals in need like these kind people did for this cow that was nearly swept away by this canal! #teamwork #animalrescue #helpanimals #saveanimals #karmagawa

node.text: ⚠️GRAPHIC IMAGES, PLEASE SHARE THIS WITH YOUR FOLLOWERS!⚠️12 years ago, the abuse of sloth bears was being sold to tourists as ‘entertainment’ in the streets of India. These ‘dancing bears’ were in constant agony as they pleased their ‘owners’ for the enjoyment of passers-by. With a rope threaded through a raw wound of their muzzle, they were pulled around to stand on their hind legs and shake in pain, giving the illusion of a ‘dance’. The bear in this video is named Raju, India's very last dancing bear. Thanks to @international_animal_rescue @wildlifesos and @freethebears more than 600 bears, including Raju were rescued and given a permanent home at one of the sanctuaries throughout India! The direct action of rescuing these bears was of course necessary in ending this 400+ year old tradition, but working with the bear handlers (known as the Kalandar people) with education and outreach programs was also vital as the Kalandar people who relied on the practice to feed their families were treated with dignity and were provided with alternate livelihoods through training schemes and grants. Many have now gone on to open their own businesses while others now work at the rescue centers. And for the first time Kalandar children were able to attend school and receive education sponsored by the project, in fact over 1000 children have now benefitted from this program. Please share this sad but ultimately uplifting post with your followers and tag people, celebrities and influencers as together, we can all make a difference to the lives of suffering animals everywhere! Great video by @international_animal_rescue #animalrescue #savethebears #endanimalcruelty #stopanimalcruelty #karmagawa

node.text: ⚠️WARNING: GRAPHIC IMAGES, PLEASE SHARE TO HELP SAVE SHARKS!⚠️ Back in 2019, the Karmagawa crew traveled to South Africa with the extremely talented underwater photographers @andremusgrove and @jeff_panella and our partners at @representclo to bring greater awareness to the sharks of South Africa since these apex predators are being killed far too often and that’s de-stabilizing our planet’s marine ecosystem. For this @savethereef project we worked with the great charity @sharkconservancy and the awesome crew at @shark_explorers and we are proud to also support marine life charities like @sharkguardian in their important shark research and conservation efforts. Please watch and share this urgent video with your followers and tag people, celebrities, influencers and news media who need to see it so we can make EVERYONE aware of how urgent this crisis has become as we MUST stop killing sharks and destroying the future of our oceans before it’s too late! #SouthAfrica #savethesharks #sharksarefriends #savethereef #karmagawa

node.title: Why We MUST Save Sharks Before It’s Too Late!

node.text: ⚠️SHARE THIS WITH SOMEONE SPECIAL IN YOUR LIFE!⚠️This is for anyone who needs a little reminder of how incredible animals are and the power of love/togetherness on this special day, Happy Valentine’s Day everyone! Share with your followers and tag someone who needs to see it too, great video by @thedodo #animallover #loveislove #valentines #happyvalentinesday #animallovers #karmagawa

⚠️GRAPHIC WARNING: PLEASE SHARE AND HELP US REMIND EVERYONE TO TAKE THESE FLOODS SERIOUSLY!⚠️ The death toll from the floods has risen to at least 205 across Europe, while a total of 176 people are still missing and now in China, 33 people have died with dozens missing even as the record-breaking rainfall continues and as authorities ramp up rescue and recovery efforts following devastating floods that caused submerged buildings, cars and even entire neighborhoods, trapped passengers in subway cars, caused landslides and overwhelmed dams and rivers. Join us in thanking the tens of thousands of brave police, firemen, good samaritans and emergency and rescue workers who have been working nonstop while risking their own lives to save people, and animals, in need. And while we continue to ask for as many prayers as possible for all those in these hard hit areas, please also use your social media platform for good and share this post wth your followers and tag people who need to see it to remind people not to underestimate these floods and to take the proper precautions to be safe — we’re seeing far too many videos of people not realizing the sheer power and force of these floods, thus endangering themselves and others around them too, SO SHARE THIS TO HELP MAKE EVERYONE AWARE OF HOW DANGEROUS THESE FLOODS ARE AND TO STAY AS SAFE AS POSSIBLE! #flashflood #flooding #climatechange #praying #prayforchina #karmagawa

node.text: ⚠️SAD BREAKING NEWS: PLEASE JOIN US IN PRAYING FOR EVERYONE IN THESE HARD HIT AREAS!⚠️ We need as many prayers as possible right now because in the last few days, over 200 people have died due to severe flash flooding in Germany, Belgium, Austria, Switzerland, Luxembourg and parts of the Netherlands with hundreds more missing and nearly 1,000 injured as Europe is suffering the worst flooding devastation in several decades. And now today, at least 12 people have died in the city of Zhengzhou, China due to record-breaking rainfall and catastrophic flooding, and more than 100,000 people have been forced to flee to seek safety. Many factors contribute to flooding, but a warming atmosphere caused by climate change makes extreme rainfall more likely so we MUST TREAT OUR PLANET BETTER BEFORE IT’S TOO LATE! Please share this post with your followers and tag people who need to see it as heavy rain is forecast to continue and we must use our social media platforms to thank all the rescue workers of their brave efforts, to pray for more survivors and make sure everyone takes the proper precautions to stay safe! #flashflood #flooding #climatechange #prayforbelgium #prayforgermany #prayforchina #karmagawa

node.text: ⚠️PLEASE SHARE WITH YOUR FOLLOWERS TO HELP END ANIMAL CRUELTY!⚠️ This video of a poor elephant in Myanmar pulling a heavy truck filled with logs chopped down from a forest has gone viral on social media because it exemplifies two urgent issues we MUST confront right now: ending both animal cruelty and deforestation! This exact kind of heartbreaking scene plays out worldwide as far too many animals are treated terribly with very little food or water and forced to perform exhausting manual labor in harsh conditions, often forced to help destroy their homes like this poor elephant is doing. WE MUST WORK TOGETHER TO STOP THIS UGLY CYCLES RIGHT NOW! Please use your social media platform for good and share this video with your followers and tag people, celebrities, influencers and news media who need to see it and share it too as we MUST all remind EVERYONE that we MUST save our forests and stop animal cruelty like this…our planet and our wildlife, especially endangered animals like this, deserve SO MUCH BETTER! Thanks for sharing @sahabatsurga #stopanimalcruelty #endanimalcruelty #animalsdeservebetter #savetheelephants #karmagawa

node.text: ⚠️GRAPHIC IMAGES, PLEASE SHARE AND HELP SPEAK UP FOR THE CUBAN PEOPLE!⚠️ We must speak up for the voiceless as Cuban special forces have been attacking and arresting civilians and now in response, the government has cut electricity and The Internet/social media to prevent the spread of protests and demonstrations, which are the biggest in decades. The Cuban government is also blocking humanitarian aid and they refuse to join COVAX, which would bring vaccines to them. This isn’t simply about COVID, but this does demonstrate clearly the cruelty of the Cuban government. CUBANS ARE BEING SILENCED SO WE MUST BE THEIR VOICE TO GET MORE INTERNATIONAL SUPPORT! Cubans will continue to fight for their freedom, but they need all the help they can get so please use your social media platform for good and share this URGENT post with your followers, tag people, celebrities, influencers and news media who need to see and share it too in order to make everyone aware of what’s happening in Cuba right now…the people there deserve SO MUCH BETTER! node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Karmagawa on July 17, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Cubans have suffered over 60 years of repression. Cubans have no freedom of assembly or freedom of speech. This week they have taken to the streets in country wide protests as many have died from COVID and are not receiving help due to the governments blocking of humanitarian aid. Cubans are currently experiencing some of the worst inflation in years. Many have died of starvation, but numbers only come in from civilians that report the deaths as the government refuses to release statistics.'.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Karmagawa on July 17, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Cuba's dictator gave the order of combat for military, police and special forces. The Cuban people do not have arms, and are defenceless against the State sanctioned violence. Protestors have now been kidnapped. Young men have been collected and are being forced to join the military. If they refuse to join, they will be tried for treason this allows for executions.'.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Karmagawa on July 17, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'The Cuban community is begging you to keep the media's eyes on our people. We are begging you to keep holding the Cuban government accountable for its crimes. The Cuban government continues to deny humanitarian aid. There are very few ways to help outside of ensuring that the plight of the Cuban people is seen and heard.'.

buttons.text: Visit the COVID-19 Information Center for vaccine resources.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Karmagawa on July 17, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'WHAT YOU CAN DO TO HELP NGO's (non-government organizations) do not exist in Cuba, so donating is difficult unless you bring in the money yourself. What you can do: Spread awareness, uplift Cuban voices, share what is happening in Cuba as most Cubans cannot without risking their lives. Petitions will not help Cuba, the regime will not listen to petitions. Protests are struck down violently, but they are taking place right now. Spreading awareness makes people feel less alone, it inspires them to fight back.'.
Photo shared by Karmagawa on July 16, 2021 tagging @bukayosaka87. May be an image of 1 person, playing a sport, standing and text that says 'SAMA 25'.

node.text: ⚠️PLEASE SHARE TO HELP STOP RACISM ON SOCIAL MEDIA!⚠️ Repost from @bukayosaka87 I have stayed away from social media for a few days to spend time with my family & reflect on the last few weeks. This message won’t do it justice how grateful I am for all the love that I have received & I feel that I need to thank everyone who has supported me. It was an honor to be part of an @England squad that leads by example, they are brothers for life & I’m grateful for everything that I have learnt from every one of the players/staff who worked so hard. To help that team reach our first final in 55 years, seeing my family in the crowd, knowing what they’ve given up to help me get there, that meant everything. There are no words to tell you how disappointed I was with the result/my penalty. I really believed we would win this for you. I’m sorry that we couldn’t bring it home for you this year, but I promise you that we will give everything we’ve got to make sure this generation knows how it feels to win. My reaction post match said it all, I was hurting so much & I felt like I’d let you all/my England family down, but I can promise you this. I will not let that moment or the negativity that I’ve received break me. For those who have campaigned on my behalf/sent me heartfelt letters, wished me /my family well - I’m so thankful. This is what football should be about. Passion, people of all races, genders, religions and backgrounds coming together with one shared joy of the rollercoaster of football. To the social media platforms @instagram @twitter @facebook I don’t want any child or adult to have to receive the hateful/hurtful messages that me Marcus and Jadon have received this week. I knew instantly the kind of hate that I was about to receive & that is a sad reality that your powerful platforms are not doing enough to stop these messages. There is no place for racism or hate of any kind in football or in any area of society & to the majority of people coming together to call out the people sending these messages, by taking action/reporting these comments to the police & by driving out the hate by being kind to one another, we will win. Love always wins. Bukayo Saka

node.text: ⚠️HELP US STOP ANIMAL PRANK VIDEOS RIGHT NOW! ⚠️ Repost from @savethereef In this video USA/Chelsea soccer star Christian Pulisic mocks an endangered and protected goliath grouper while showing off for social media. Cruel and unnecessary animal prank videos like this MUST STOP as no living creature, let alone any endangered species, should be used for entertainment and we all work together to spread awareness about this issue right now! Atlantic Goliath groupers, which grow up to more than eight feet long and can weigh up to about 800 pounds, are recognized as a vulnerable species, decreasing in population, by the International Union for Conservation of Nature (IUCN) and referring to the Florida Fish and Wildlife Conservation Commission rules, which state that photos of this species should not delay release in any way, @blueplanetsociety said: “in our opinion Christian Pulisic's stunt was in clear breach of these rules. Animal abuse to attract attention for social media videos appears to be on the increase. We believe strongly that people should be called out for it, especially when they are as influential as Mr Pulisic." So please share this video with your followers and tag people, celebrities & influencers who need to see and share this too and let’s remind EVERYONE that we must treat wildlife FAR BETTER…athletes/celebrities like Christian, who millions of people look up to, should use their influence to encourage people to respect not disrespect wildlife like this! #fisharefriends #respectwildlife #animalsdeservebetter #karmagawa #savethereef

node.text: ⚠️GRAPHIC IMAGES, PLEASE SHARE AND SIGN NEW PETITION AS THESE POOR DOGS DESERVE BETTER!⚠️ This really needs to be brought to EVERYONE’S attention for anything to change! MBR Acres in Cambridgeshire is a GOVERNMENT RAN breeding ground for over 2000 Beagles where they are then taken to labs to be experimented on, tortured and killed everyday…Just because they’re a calm and beautifully natured breed? This is animal exploitation and it is WRONG! By this point I am absolutely disgusted with the human race and how anybody with a heart could allow this to happen?! We are in the 21st century this should not be happening! How do these people sleep at night!? Shame on them! These poor dogs do not have a voice but we do! I urge people to sign the petition linked in the @karmagawa bio and also share this important post with your followers, tag people, celebrities, influencers and news media who need to see and share it too in order to raise awareness and help save these innocent animals, it takes 2 seconds, repost from @chloemae31 #campbeagle #mbrbeagles #stopanimaltesting #animalcruelty #savethesedogs

node.text: ⚠️SAD BREAKING NEWS: PLEASE SHARE AND SIGN THE PETITION TO STOP THIS ANIMAL ABUSE RIGHT NOW! ⚠️ We are angry beyond belief with the news that despite ongoing legal action, the Comunidad de Madrid has lifted the suspension on animal tests at Vivotecnia and that tests at this barbaric facility responsible for shocking cruelty and animal suffering, in breach of European and Spanish law, might never have fully stopped in the first place. The testing of baby pigs, beagles, rabbits, monkeys, rats and mice reveals deliberate cruelty, rabbits dying, monkeys screaming and dogs suffering accompanied by staff jokes as they are injected or forced to ingest or inhale substances to measure toxic effects, which can include vomiting, internal bleeding, respiratory problems, fever, organ failure and even death.⁠ THIS IS SO WRONG, THESE POOR ANIMALS DESERVE BETTER! Please urgently sign and share the petition linked in the @karmagawa bio and  highlights calling for Madrid authorities to revoke Vivotecnia’s license and close the laboratory so we can hit the crucial 1 million voices milestone demanding to end the suffering! Use your social media platform for good and share this important post with your followers and tag people, celebrities and influencers who need to see this and share too as WE MUST WORK TOGETHER TO STOP THIS ANIMAL ABUSE RIGHT NOW! Please share and use your social media platform and speak up for these innocent animals that are being tortured! Images by @crueltyfreeintl⁠ #endanimalcruelty #stopanimalcruelty #animaltesting #endanimaltesting #vivotecnia #stopanimaltesting #animalsdeservebetter #karmagawa

node.text: ⚠️URGENT ISSUE, PLEASE SHARE TO HELP SPREAD AWARENESS!⚠️ Repost from @savethereef This man was caught littering a river with thousands of plastic water bottles and while he’s been arrested and faces up to a year in jail for his water pollution, his crime will impact wildlife and the environment for centuries since plastic does not decompose quickly. Police are also still searching for his accomplices so let’s all share this video to help the police find the other polluters in this video! And what’s worse is that this same kind of irresponsible polluting is carried by countless individuals and companies worldwide so much so that by 2050 it’s estimated there will be 900+ million tons of plastic in the ocean which is more than the weight of all the fish in the sea! It’s just absolutely heartbreaking to see and our beaches, oceans, rivers and birds, animals and marine life deserve better SO WE MUST STOP THIS RIGHT NOW! Please use your social media platform for good and share this important post with your followers and tag people, celebrities, influencers and news media who need to see it so they can share too & let’s all spread awareness about this URGENT issue and condemn disgusting polluting like this before it’s too late! Video by @get.waste.ed #plasticpollution #stoplittering #karmagawa #savethereef

⚠️CRAZY WEATHER: PLEASE SHARE AND HELP US REMIND PEOPLE TO STAY SAFE/TAKE THIS STORM SERIOUSLY!⚠️ Heavy rains caused massive flooding in New York and also at several NY train stations — forcing some desperate people to wade through waist-deep waters on their daily commute! Police have rescued dozens people trapped by the flash floods so far and flash flood watches are now in effect for over 50 million Americans in New York, New Jersey and Connecticut all day Friday. The US east coast has been battered by extreme weather this week as heavy thunderstorms brought this widespread flooding to New York, while Tropical Storm Elsa dumped heavy rainfall and even sparked tornadoes in North Carolina and Georgia. NYC is expected to continue getting drenched today, when Tropical Storm Elsa moves through the region. Please join us in praying for all those in this storm’s path and share this with your followers and tag people, celebrities and influencers who need to see and share this too as we must remind everyone to stay safe and take these flood warnings seriously! Videos by @whatisnewyork @subwaycreatures #flashflood #climatechange #staysafe #karmagawa

node.text: ⚠️PLEASE SHARE WITH YOUR FOLLOWERS TO HELP END THIS ANIMAL CRUELTY!⚠️ This poor horse in Florence, Italy had enough. She’s been forced to carry the weight of far too many humans for far too long and during one scorching hot day, she finally was at her breaking point and rebelled, fighting to free herself from all the abuse she’s endured over the years. WE MUST STOP forcing innocent animals to carry so much weight to the point of exhaustion, especially during the grueling summer months! We MUST stop this animal cruelty right now and learn to respect these beautiful creatures much more! When will enough people finally work together to speak up for the voiceless? THE TIME IS NOW! Please join us in making this a better world for animals by using your social media platform to spread awareness about this URGENT issue, share this post with your followers and tag people, celebrities, influencers and new media who need to see this and share it too because animals deserve SO MUCH BETTER! Thanks for sharing @napolianimalsave #helpanimals #animalsdeservebetter #stopanimalabuse #stopanimalcruelty #endanimalcruelty #karmagawa

node.text: ⚠️SAD BREAKING NEWS, PLEASE SHARE AS WE MUST TREAT OUR PLANET BETTER!⚠️ Storm-producing fire clouds sparked hundreds of thousands of lightning strikes over wildfire-stricken British Columbia and northwestern Alberta provinces in Canada the past few days, shocking meteorologists. The North American Lightning Detection Network recorded an astounding 710,177 lightning events across British Columbia and northwestern Alberta in a span of just 15 hours, and out of those there were 112,803 cloud-to-ground strikes detected over the same area. “I’ve watched a lot of wildfire-associated events during the satellite era, and I think this might be the singularly most extreme I've ever seen,” said Daniel Swain, a climate scientist at UCLA. The majority of the strikes in western Canada were the result of pyrocumulonimbus clouds forming over the wildfires tearing across western Canada, which has also suffered from a sweltering heat wave in the past week. Rising temperatures and drier air are associated with more frequent and more intense wildfires. And as wildfires increase in size and severity, fire-generated storms, too, are becoming more common. Please share this post with your followers and tag people, celebrities, influencers and new media who need to see this and share it too, these storms and fires are getting worse every year so we MUST change how we treat our planet before it’s too late! #fireclouds #storms #wildfires #britishcolumbia #karmagawa
